                    <div class="client-coupon-benefit">
                      <div class="client-coupon-benefit-icon">⚡</div>
                      <span>Vale para <strong>seguidores, curtidas e views</strong></span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="client-coupon-divider"></div>
